{
  "texts": [
    "We finetune the SDXL foot_0 model (Podell et al., 2023) via LoRA and MoSLoRA.",
    "In MoSLoRA, the mixer is initialized as an orthogonal matrix.",
    "During finetuning, the learning rate is 1e-4, and the batch size is 4.",
    "We train the model for 500 steps, which costs around 16 minutes using 1 80G A100 GPU.",
    "During generation, we infer 50 steps for the given prompts."
  ]
}